name: @typed/fp
description: Data Structures and Resources for fp-ts

scripts.build: npm run check:ts-patch && npm run build:typescript && concurrently 'npm:build:packages' 'npm:update:package-exports'
scripts.docs: rimraf docs && concurrently npm:docs:api && git add docs && git commit -m 'docs: regenerate docs'
scripts.preversion: npm test && npm run update && npm run build
